near Amphipolis. When she was 4, she met up with a young Eve (FreakyRebelGrl). At the age of 7
the village was destroyed and she
was taken to Rome as a slave.
After enduring eight years of
slavery, she killed the man who
held her freedom and eventually
made her way back to Greece. She met up with Eve (then Livia) at 19 and joined up in her army, growing closer and closer to the girl. When Livia became good again, Robin went back with her and Xena and Gabrielle to Greece.
At 24, she was found by Queen
Varia Avande and ended up making her way to Chadesia. She is very much so mortal, but has the ability to both speak to and understand animals, mainly horses 
though. She's very defiant, not much of a people person, but is sweet once you get to know her. She believes in loyalty even if a person has to sacrifice their life
to fulfill it. 
She and Eve now have a five year old daughter, Kayla Morgan, and a five month old baby girl, Ravyn Daine.</span></div>	</div> 	<div id="contactinfo">		<h2>My Contact Information</h2>		<div id="email"><span class="title">Email Address ::</span>  <span class="privatevalue">private</span></div>		<div id="pm">		<span class="title">My Inbox ::</span> 						<span class="value"><a href="" title="Send a message using the ezboard inbox feature" >Send me a Message!</a></span>				</div>		<div id="im"><span class="title">IM ::</span> <span class="value">AOL - Redrobin443</span></div>		<div id="link"><span class="title">Personal Link ::</span> <span class="value"><a href="http://members.shaw.ca/wpgclan/whatyouare.htm" target="_blank">What You Are...</a></span></div>		<div id="recentposts"><span class="title">Recent Posts ::</span> 										<span class="value">		<dl>				<dt><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm25.showMessage?topicID=77.topic&index=5" title="post" target="_blank">Re: Bard in Ephesus</a></dt>		<dd><em>from <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm25" title="forum the above post is in" target="_blank">Amazons Loyal to Artemis</a></em></dd>				<dt><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm25.showMessage?topicID=77.topic&index=3" title="post" target="_blank">Re: Bard in Ephesus</a></dt>		<dd><em>from <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm25" title="forum the above post is in" target="_blank">Amazons Loyal to Artemis</a></em></dd>				<dt><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm49.showMessage?topicID=3.topic" title="post" target="_blank">Thanks for a blessing</a></dt>		<dd><em>from <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm49" title="forum the above post is in" target="_blank">*Temple of Artemis at Ephesus</a></em></dd>				<dt><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm25.showMessage?topicID=77.topic&index=1" title="post" target="_blank">Re